---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About The WEL Foundation">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-6) 0;">
    
    <header style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6); text-align:center;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue);">About Us</h1>
    </header>
    <section>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>The WEL Foundation is determined to treat the whole individual from the inside out without judgment. We respect every individual and strive to provide the most practical and empowering mental health interventions available.</p>
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>Based in Baltimore, we specialize in Psychiatric Rehabilitation Programs (PRP), Substance Use Disorder (SUD) therapy, and comprehensive Community Development initiatives. We believe that with the right guidance, mental health challenges should not serve as unbreachable barriers.</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
